    <!-- Consonants Section -->
    <section id="consonants" class="consonanats-section">
        <h3><mark>About Consonants</h3>
            <p class="about-text">
                There are 19 consonants in Korean and we can divide it in 3 parts.

            </p>
            <b>Plain Consonants, Aspirated Consonants and double consonants</b>
            <p>- Plain Consonants : "„Ñ± „Ñ¥ „Ñ∑ „Ñπ „ÖÅ „ÖÇ „ÖÖ „Öá „Öà „Öé"<br> - Aspirated Consonants : "„Öã „Öå „Öç „Öä"<br>- Double Consonants
                :
                "„Ñ≤ „Öå „ÖÉ „ÖÜ „Öâ" </p>

            <table border='1'>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td> Plain Consonants </td>
